rows.label: tlk4240008101_msg0001
rows.name:
Hah hah hah!
Witness mighty power of science!

rows.label: tlk4240008101_msg0002
rows.name:
Kyukyu used to work in Acedia, but
now have nothing. No lab, no tools,
no money!

rows.label: tlk4240008101_msg0003
rows.name:
Had to make do with research here,
crushing, mixing, and burning...

rows.label: tlk4240008101_msg0004
rows.name:
But cost of research just too high...
Kyukyu want to study with roof over
head!

rows.label: tlk4240008101_msg0005
rows.name:
All Kyukyu want is to make use of
abilities and earn decent living with
research!
